      <p id="trust-tldr-body">TechBrot&rsquo;s trust rests on <strong>four verifiable pillars</strong>. <strong>Credentials:</strong> <a href="/quickbooks/proadvisor-team/">Certified Intuit QuickBooks ProAdvisors</a> across QBO Level 2, Desktop, Enterprise, and Payroll &mdash; Intuit&rsquo;s public ProAdvisor directory lists active ProAdvisors for verification. <strong>Accountability:</strong> every engagement is fixed-fee with written scope, owned end-to-end by a named ProAdvisor. <strong>Security:</strong> bank-level encryption, accountant-user access inside your own QuickBooks file, no data export required, audit trail always visible to you. <strong>Independence:</strong> an independent ProAdvisor firm &mdash; not affiliated with Intuit Inc. &mdash; so recommendations follow your business needs, not vendor incentives.</p>
