    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">Four pillars. All verifiable.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 28px;max-width:70ch;">Trust in accounting can&rsquo;t rest on adjectives. It rests on things you can check. These four pillars are the foundation &mdash; each backed by something verifiable, not asserted.</p>
    <div class="r-2">
      <div class="dc-card">
        <span class="eyebrow" style="display:block;margin-bottom:8px;">01</span>
        <h3>Credentials</h3>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;">Certified Intuit QuickBooks ProAdvisors across <strong>all four core platforms</strong> &mdash; QBO Level 2, Desktop, Enterprise, Payroll. Renewed annually through Intuit testing.</p>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:8px 0 0;"><strong>How to verify:</strong> Search Intuit&rsquo;s public ProAdvisor directory at proadvisor.intuit.com by firm name. Active status = current credentials.</p>
        <a class="hub-card__go" href="/quickbooks/proadvisor-team/">The ProAdvisor team <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 12h15M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></a>
      </div>
      <div class="dc-card">
        <span class="eyebrow" style="display:block;margin-bottom:8px;">02</span>
        <h3>Accountability</h3>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;">Every engagement is <strong>fixed-fee with written scope</strong> before any work begins. A <strong>named ProAdvisor owns your account end-to-end</strong> &mdash; same person scopes, delivers, and handles ongoing work.</p>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:8px 0 0;"><strong>How it&rsquo;s structural:</strong> The written scope is the standard. Work that doesn&rsquo;t match is corrected at no cost. No hourly billing, no scope creep, no account-manager rotation.</p>
        <a class="hub-card__go" href="/accounting/services/">Engagement standards <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 12h15M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></a>
      </div>
      <div class="dc-card">
        <span class="eyebrow" style="display:block;margin-bottom:8px;">03</span>
        <h3>Security</h3>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;">We work as an <strong>accountant-user inside your own QuickBooks file</strong> &mdash; your data, your access controls, grantable and revocable by you at any time. <strong>No data export to a parallel system.</strong></p>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:8px 0 0;"><strong>What protects you:</strong> Encrypted screen-share and file transfers. QuickBooks audit trail visible to you at all times. Access logged. You hold the keys.</p>
        <a class="hub-card__go" href="/legal/dpa/">Data processing terms <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 12h15M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></a>
      </div>
      <div class="dc-card">
        <span class="eyebrow" style="display:block;margin-bottom:8px;">04</span>
        <h3>Independence</h3>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;">An <strong>independent ProAdvisor firm</strong> &mdash; not owned, employed, or operated by Intuit Inc. QuickBooks is a registered trademark of Intuit Inc.</p>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:8px 0 0;"><strong>Why it&rsquo;s a feature:</strong> Independence means recommendations follow <strong>your business needs</strong>, not vendor incentives. We recommend the platform that fits &mdash; QBO, Enterprise, or something else entirely &mdash; not the one we&rsquo;d earn more on.</p>
        <a class="hub-card__go" href="/about/">About TechBrot <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 12h15M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></a>
