{#- STANDARDS — 6 (baseline h3s). sand alt. -#}
<section class="sec reveal hub-rt--alt" id="trust-standards" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Accountability in practice</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">The standards every engagement runs to.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 28px;max-width:70ch;">Accountability isn&rsquo;t a promise &mdash; it&rsquo;s an operating model. Every engagement, direct or network, runs to these six standards.</p>
    <div class="r-3">
      <div class="dc-card"><span class="eyebrow" style="display:block;margin-bottom:8px;">01</span><h3>Free discovery call</h3><p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;">Every engagement begins with a <strong>30-minute discovery call</strong>. Free, no obligation. We surface the right engagement &mdash; or honestly say we&rsquo;re not the right fit.</p></div>
      <div class="dc-card"><span class="eyebrow" style="display:block;margin-bottom:8px;">02</span><h3>Written fixed-fee scope</h3><p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;"><strong>Written scope within 3 business days</strong> of the call. Fixed fee. No hourly billing. If work expands, scope is rewritten and re-approved.</p></div>
      <div class="dc-card"><span class="eyebrow" style="display:block;margin-bottom:8px;">03</span><h3>Certified ProAdvisor delivery</h3><p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;">Delivered by a <strong>Certified Intuit ProAdvisor</strong> &mdash; not a general bookkeeper, not an offshore queue. Intuit&rsquo;s public ProAdvisor directory lists active ProAdvisors for verification.</p></div>
      <div class="dc-card"><span class="eyebrow" style="display:block;margin-bottom:8px;">04</span><h3>Named-operator continuity</h3><p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;">A <strong>named ProAdvisor owns your account end-to-end</strong>. No account-manager rotation. No re-explaining your business each quarter.</p></div>
      <div class="dc-card"><span class="eyebrow" style="display:block;margin-bottom:8px;">05</span><h3>Direct file access</h3><p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;">We work <strong>inside your QuickBooks file</strong> as accountant-users. Your books, your data, your audit trail. Never a parallel system, never forced data export.</p></div>
      <div class="dc-card"><span class="eyebrow" style="display:block;margin-bottom:8px;">06</span><h3>CPA-ready handoff</h3><p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;">Recurring engagements include <strong>year-end CPA handoff at no additional cost</strong>. Tax-prep files and schedules delivered to your CPA on their timeline.</p></div>
