    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Honest scope</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">What we do, don't do, and coordinate.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 28px;max-width:70ch;">Trust includes being honest about limits. Here&rsquo;s the clean read &mdash; stated up front, not buried.</p>
    <div class="r-3">
      <div class="dc-card"><h3>We do</h3><p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;">Bookkeeping (monthly, cleanup, catch-up). QuickBooks setup, cleanup, migration. Payroll management. Multi-state sales tax compliance. Fractional CFO. CPA-ready year-end handoff. State and local jurisdiction tax operational configuration.</p></div>
      <div class="dc-card"><h3>We don't</h3><p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;">File federal or state tax returns. Represent clients before the IRS or state agencies. Provide Intuit&rsquo;s software-level technical support. Publish unverified testimonials or inflated performance claims.</p></div>
      <div class="dc-card"><h3>We coordinate with</h3><p class="prose" style="font-size:14.5px;margin:6px 0 0;">Your existing CPA or EA for tax filings. Your tax counsel for audit defense. Sales tax counsel for state-specific tax-position work. We refer to licensed practitioners when scope requires it.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

